  ('lulu',        'blitzcrank', 3, 'If Lulu gets hooked, she needs to use Whimsy defensively and loses offensive value.'),
  ('lulu',        'leona',      3, 'Leona''s all-in is fast enough to kill Lulu before polymorph interrupts it.'),
