  ('brand',       'blitzcrank', 3, 'Brand is immobile. Hook removes him from his poke range and kills him.'),
  ('nami',        'blitzcrank', 3, 'Nami has no escape from a Blitz hook. Gets hooked, dies, lane is over.'),
  ('vel-koz',     'blitzcrank', 4, 'Vel''Koz is completely immobile. Blitz hook is almost always a kill.'),
  ('leona',       'janna',      3, 'Janna ult pushes Leona away and knocks everyone up, completely negating her engage.'),
  ('leona',       'lulu',       3, 'Lulu polymorph cancels Leona''s engage entirely. Times right, it shuts her down.'),
  ('alistar',     'nautilus',   3, 'Nautilus hook into CC chain counters Alistar''s combo timing completely.'),
  ('blitzcrank',  'thresh',     3, 'Thresh can hook targets that Blitz misses and offers more CC variety.'),
